import { Box, Flex, FormControl, HStack } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import Cour from "../atoms/form/Cour"
import YearInput from "../atoms/form/YearInput"

const Search = () => {
    return (
        <Flex w='100%' pt='40px'>
            <FormControl>
                <Flex justify='center' align='center' >
                    <HStack>
                    <Box>
                        <YearInput />
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Cour />
                    </Box>
                    </HStack>
                </Flex>
            </FormControl>
        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Search
